<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 6. Lonchodraco (?) microdon comb. n. A-F holotype CAMSM B 54486 (Albian, Cambridge Greensand), anterior fragment of the rostrum A ventral view B respective line drawing C anterior view D respective line drawing E posterior view F respective line drawing. In B dashed lines indicate the portion lost since the original description G-L referred specimen CAMSM B 54439 (Albian, Cambridge Greensand), anterior fragment of the rostrum G ventral view H respective line drawing I anterior view J respective line drawing K posterior view L respective line drawing. Abbreviation: prid - palatal ridge. Arrows indicate alveoli or teeth. Scale bar = 10 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/22074" .

